<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>dāng wǒ jiāng sǐ zài láng de kǒu 迦南483</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 dāng wǒ jiāng sǐ zài láng de kǒu, shì zhǔ lái bǎ wǒ zhěng jiù.
 yòu zǒu guò rén shēng měi gè lù kǒu, dōu yǒu tā cí ài shuāng shǒu.
 tā dòng chá wǒ de xīn líng shēn chù, bù róng yǒu bàn diǎn wū gòu.
 ràng wǒ chéng wèi xīn zào de rén, yòng xiào liǎn huà nán jiě yōu.
 bù yào wèi míng tiān dān yōu, zhǔ shì nǐ zuì qīn péng yǒu.
 zǒng shì zài wú zhù de shí hòu, shēn chū tā dīng hén shuāng shǒu.
 bù yào wèi qián tú dān yōu, zhǔ shì wǒ zuì qīn péng yǒu.
 zǒng shì zài jué wàng de shí hòu, xiǎn chū tā de fù yǒu.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>483</hymn_number>
</song>